text: Luboš Brchel (7 March 1920 - 31 October 1981) was a Slovak alpine skier. He competed in three events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Slovak male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kladno
